      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1">
		Prosperity! Fortune!
	</p>
        <p n="2-4">
		<unclear>Tirthy</unclear>-second year of the victorious king Kampavikramvarman.
	</p>
        <p n="4-9">
		To Kāṭantai Nakkaṉ Caṭaiyaṉ of this village, we, the villagers of Kāviṭu we have given after selling <gap reason="undefined"/>
	</p>
        <p n="9-12">
		He who destroys this pious act <supplied reason="undefined">will incur</supplied> the sin of he does that between the Ganges and Kumari.
	</p>
